# Contact form — Formspree (no custom domain or Resend required)
# 1. Create a form at https://formspree.io
# 2. Add all team emails under Formspree “Notifications”
# 3. Paste your form endpoint here and restart the dev server / redeploy:

# No space before/after the = sign.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ = included in the browser bundle (required so the form can POST). Formspree URLs are
# meant to be public — turn on CAPTCHA / domain restrictions in the Formspree dashboard if you need extra abuse protection.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_URL=https://formspree.io/f/xxxxxxxx
